113
00:06:23,810 --> 00:06:26,860
♪Flowing through my fingers,
each note brings sorrow♪

114
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:30,190
♪The flowers fall;
the music of the night grows cold♪

115
00:06:30,830 --> 00:06:35,460
♪Playing with my hair, gazing deeply,
waiting for someone♪

116
00:07:02,420 --> 00:07:03,570
Now I announce

117
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:06,420
