118
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,910
Li Wanjun, Miss Li.

119
00:07:09,190 --> 00:07:11,940
She solved 20 riddles.

120
00:07:13,260 --> 00:07:14,940
Mr. Zhou, this should be yours.

121
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:16,460
