125
00:07:24,870 --> 00:07:26,090
Miss Li, please.

126
00:07:34,020 --> 00:07:34,940
Miss Wanjun,

127
00:07:35,180 --> 00:07:37,660
Tongque Tavern will provide you

128
00:07:37,740 --> 00:07:39,220
