Help! Help! Help!

151
00:08:59,850 --> 00:09:00,690
Help!

152
00:09:00,700 --> 00:09:02,060
- Mr. Gu.
- Canghai.

153
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:03,560
Are you alright?

154
00:09:03,700 --> 00:09:04,540
I'm fine.

155
00:09:04,560 --> 00:09:05,400
Let's go.

156
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:08,050
Mr. Gu, hurry.

157
00:09:08,270 --> 00:09:09,110
Mr. Gu, hurry.

158
